    "body": "Using 0.29.12\r\n\r\n```\r\ncdef double[::1, :] my_array = view.array(shape=(0, 5), itemsize=sizeof(double), format=\"d\", mode=\"fortran\")\r\n```\r\n\r\nAbove code will raise an exception.\r\n\r\nI need this feature for my rule based machine learning algo, in which some rule may result an empty output.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
